text: Muradym () is a rural locality (a village) in Yuldybayevsky Selsoviet, Kugarchinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 165 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 27 km from Mrakovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kugarchinsky District
title: Muradym, Kugarchinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
